info.name: Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dark chocolate sponge cake is layered with vanilla whipped cream and dark cherry compote, then finished with dark chocolate shavings and red cherries. It?s a classic Black Forest recipe.

info.name: German Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Multiple layers of German dark chocolate sponge are topped with light chocolate cream, vanilla cream, and infused with dark and sour cherry compote. It is finished with a cherry and choco curls. The darker, more sour cherries make it an authentic German Black Forest cake recipe.

info.name: Blueberry Bake Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | A light and creamy cheesecake slice made with cream cheese and topped with blueberry compote.

info.name: Chocolate Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dark chocolate sponge cake is layered with chocolate ganache and topped with chocolate sponge crumbs.

info.name: Red Velvet Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | This jar cake features a sponge infused with natural beetroot color and cream cheese frosting, along with red velvet crumbs. We have recreated the original recipe that originated in the United States.

info.name: Eggless Classic Walnut Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | An eggless brownie made with high-quality couverture chocolate, cocoa, walnut butter, fresh cream, and chunks of real walnuts that add a delightful crunch.

info.name: Eggless Nutella Hazelnut Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic eggless chocolate brownie blended with Nutella spread, topped with chunks of hazelnuts. The chocolate used is high-quality couverture chocolate.

info.name: Butterscotch Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | Our classic butterscotch cake but as a pastry. The base is a vanilla sponge cake topped with caramel cream, candied butterscotch nuts, and a drizzle of caramel sauce. This is a classic butterscotch recipe.

info.name: Black Forest Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | A moist chocolate sponge cake features two distinct layers: soft, creamy chocolate cream and vanilla whipped cream with dark cherry compote. It is then topped with chocolate flakes and a cherry.

info.name: Blueberry Cup Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Fresh blueberry pulp topped with whipped cream & sprinkles in a cup cake

info.name: Vanilla Cup Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic cupcake with vanilla whippd cream adn edible sugar sprinkles

info.name: Mango Jar Cake (180ml)
info.description: Serves 1 | A refreshing 180ml jar cake layered with moist sponge and creamy mango mousse. Bursting with tropical flavor, it's the perfect single-serve treat for mango lovers.

info.name: Mango Naked Cake (500gm)
info.description: Serves 6 | A light and fruity 500gm Mango Naked Cake, layered with fresh cream and real mango chunks. Minimal on frosting, big on tropical flavor?perfect for summer celebrations or a sweet, simple indulgence.

info.name: Mango Mousse Cake (500gm)
info.description: Serves 6 | A light, airy mousse cake made with velvety mascarpone cheese, soft vanilla sponge, and layers of tangy mango compote and smooth mango pur?e, topped with fresh mango chunks ? a cake created to perfection!

info.name: Choco Truffle Cake
info.description: Serves 6 | A rich cocoa sponge cake is layered with dark chocolate ganache and finished with a silky chocolate glaze.

info.name: Choco Crunch KitKat Cake
info.description: Serves 6 | A moist chocolate cake layered with crunchy KitKat? pieces. Every forkful is filled with smooth, rich chocolate and satisfying crispy bites.

info.name: Choco Vanilla Cake
info.description: Serves 6 | A four-layer vanilla sponge cake is layered with chocolate truffle, topped with a vanilla glaze and dark chocolate truffle. The cake is finished with a white chocolate garnish and a cherry.

info.name: Pineapple Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A vanilla sponge base is topped with a generous layer of freshly cooked pineapple compote, vanilla whipped cream, and finished with chocolate pieces and a cherry.

info.name: Fresh Fruit Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A vanilla sponge base is topped with freshly whipped vanilla custard cream and an assortment of thinly sliced seasonal fresh fruits. It is finished with vanilla cream and toasted almond flakes, which give it a subtle almondy aftertaste.

info.name: Butterscotch Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A vanilla sponge cake is layered with fresh caramel cream and butterscotch crumble, then finished with caramel glaze and cake crumb dressing on the sides. It?s a classic butterscotch recipe.

info.name: Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dark chocolate sponge cake is layered with vanilla whipped cream and dark cherry compote, then finished with dark chocolate shavings and red cherries. It?s a classic Black Forest recipe.

info.name: German Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Multiple layers of German dark chocolate sponge are topped with light chocolate cream, vanilla cream, and infused with dark and sour cherry compote. It is finished with a cherry and choco curls. The darker, more sour cherries make it an authentic German Black Forest cake recipe.

info.name: Chocolate Dream Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A combination of chocolate sponge and chocolate mousse, topped with a chocolate disk dusted in cocoa powder. Break through the top layer with a spoon to dive into this dreamy creation of chocolate Dream Cake.

info.name: Belgian Chocolate Cake (600 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A chocolate sponge base is layered with dark chocolate mousse and a crunchy French biscuit. The cake is topped with a light chocolate drop and a chocolate garnish - a recipe that originated in Europe.

info.name: Ferrero Rocher Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | This gourmet delight is crafted with milk chocolate, Nutella, hazelnuts, and 100% real, fresh cream. It is then garnished with Ferrero Rochers - a perfect tribute to classic chocolate.

info.name: Nutella Hazelnut Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A chocolate sponge base is layered with chocolate hazelnut mousse, dark chocolate, milk chocolate fresh cream, and molten Nutella.

info.name: Trio Mousse Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | This gourmet cake features three layers of mousse - milk chocolate, white chocolate, and dark chocolate. The top layer is made of chocolate truffle and is garnished with a golden leaf and a milk chocolate decoration. This recipe originated in Europe.

info.name: Coffee Opera Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A square almond sponge base made with eggs and rich chocolate ganache is soaked in filtered coffee syrup and coffee buttercream, then topped with our signature Opera glaze. This recipe is an authentic French classic.

info.name: Tiramisu Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A sponge cake soaked in espresso coffee is layered with mascarpone cheese, topped with freshly whipped cream, and dusted with cocoa. This dessert is infused with a hint of alcohol and is a perfect choice to sweeten any moment. This is Bakingo?s rendition of a classic Italian tiramisu recipe.

info.name: New York Bake Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | Cheesecake made with high concentration of cream cheese with dense and rich texture. A recipe originated in USA.

info.name: Blueberry Bake Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | A light and creamy cheesecake slice made with cream cheese and topped with blueberry compote.

info.name: Biscoff Baked Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic Belgian Biscoff cheesecake in slice form. The cheese base is topped with Biscoff spread and infused with a Lotus Biscoff biscuit.

info.name: Nutella Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | Cheesecake crafted with cream cheese and topped with Nutella - a dreamy combination come true.

info.name: Blueberry Baked Cheesecake (600 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | Classic cheesecake made with cream cheese and fresh cream, paired with a fresh blueberry compote.

info.name: Biscoff Baked Cheesecake (600 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | Cheesecake base topped with Biscoff spread and a Lotus Biscoff biscuit. It's a classic Belgian recipe.

info.name: Choco Mud Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dark chocolate sponge cake is layered with light chocolate cream and chocolate ganache, resulting in a rich, mud-like texture.

info.name: Chocolate Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dark chocolate sponge cake is layered with chocolate ganache and topped with chocolate sponge crumbs.

info.name: Red Velvet Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | This jar cake features a sponge infused with natural beetroot color and cream cheese frosting, along with red velvet crumbs. We have recreated the original recipe that originated in the United States.

info.name: Chocolate Hazelnut Caramel Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | The base is a rich chocolate sponge cake topped with a chocolate ganache made in-house. We then add a sticky toffee caramel syrup and a blend of hazelnuts for a delightful crunch.

info.name: Choco Crunch Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A chocolate sponge cake is topped with a layer of chocolate truffle ganache. Chocolate chips and bits of butterscotch are blended between the layers to add a delightful crunch.

info.name: Banoffee Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | The base is made entirely of crushed cookies made in-house. It is then topped with a thick caramel sauce, sliced bananas, vanilla cream, and garnished with chocolate flakes.

info.name: Nutella Hazelnut Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A chocolate sponge base blended with molten Nutella, truffle, and fresh hazelnuts is topped with fresh cream in a jar. The cream is 100% real and fresh, and the chocolate is made in-house (eggless). This is Bakingo's rendition of the original Nutella hazelnut recipe.

info.name: Belgian Chocolate Mousse Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | The base is a chocolate sponge cake topped with silken Belgian dark chocolate mousse (made with 45% dark chocolate ganache) and garnished with chocolate flakes.

info.name: Biscoff Cheesecake Jar
info.description: Serves 1 | A creamy baked cheesecake sits atop a cookie crumb base in a jar, topped with Lotus Biscoff spread and garnished with a Lotus biscuit. This is a classic European recipe.

info.name: Eggless Classic Walnut Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | An eggless brownie made with high-quality couverture chocolate, cocoa, walnut butter, fresh cream, and chunks of real walnuts that add a delightful crunch.

info.name: Eggless Nutella Hazelnut Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic eggless chocolate brownie blended with Nutella spread, topped with chunks of hazelnuts. The chocolate used is high-quality couverture chocolate.

info.name: Eggless Millionaire Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic eggless chocolate brownie featuring a molten, gooey layer of caramel made in-house, topped with a layer of chocolate ganache made with high-quality couverture chocolate and fresh cream.

info.name: Eggless Double Choco Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic eggless chocolate brownie made with double the chocolate, fresh cream, and chunks of high-quality couverture chocolate.

info.name: Choco Truffle Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | A moist chocolate sponge cake is topped with a rich and creamy ganache made from whipped cream, real couverture chocolate, and a blend of truffles, then garnished with milk chocolate crispies.

info.name: Pineapple Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | A vanilla sponge cake is topped with whipped vanilla cream, homemade pineapple compote, and chunks of fresh pineapple.

info.name: Butterscotch Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | Our classic butterscotch cake but as a pastry. The base is a vanilla sponge cake topped with caramel cream, candied butterscotch nuts, and a drizzle of caramel sauce. This is a classic butterscotch recipe.

info.name: Kit Kat Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | A soft, chocolate-filled KitKat? pastry, crowned with KitKat chunks and a bar, giving you the ultimate sweet and crunchy treat.

info.name: Red Velvet Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | A rich vanilla sponge cake forms the base, blended with whipped cream, red velvet crumbs, and cream cheese frosting. We use beetroot for color, with no artificial colors. This is the original Red Velvet recipe that originated in the United States.

info.name: Black Forest Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | A moist chocolate sponge cake features two distinct layers: soft, creamy chocolate cream and vanilla whipped cream with dark cherry compote. It is then topped with chocolate flakes and a cherry.

info.name: Chocolate Chip Pastry
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic chocolate chip cake recipe presented as a pastry. A rich chocolate sponge cake is layered with soft, silken chocolate cream and chocolate chips, finished with a chocolate glaze, and garnished with chocolate cream.

info.name: Rose Tres Leches
info.description: Serves 1 | A luscious rose-flavored Tres Leches cake, soaked in a trio of sweet milks and adorned with delicate rose petals.

info.name: Choco Lava
info.description: Serves 1 | The classic Choco lava cake Bakingo style. Gooey molten CHD 45 chocolaty goodness.

info.name: Vanilla Cup Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic cupcake with vanilla whippd cream adn edible sugar sprinkles

info.name: Red Velvet Cup Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A red velvet extravaganza topped with whippe cream and red velvet sprinkles

info.name: Coffee Cup Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Deliciously baked Coffee Cupcakes frosted with a buttercream swirl, topped with a chocolate ball and dusted with coffee powder.

info.name: Choco Chip Cream Cup Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic chocolate cream cup cake overloaded with choco chips

info.name: Marble Tea Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Marble Tea Cake is a light, moist cake with a beautiful swirl of chocolate and vanilla flavors, offering a delightful treat perfect as a marble tea cake.

info.name: Fruit Nut & Cranberry Tea Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Fruit Nut & Cranberry Tea Cake is a moist, flavorful cake packed with a mix of dried fruits, nuts, and cranberries, making it a deliciously festive treat, perfect as a fruit nut & cranberry tea cake.

info.name: Multigrain Tea Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Multigrain Tea Cake is a wholesome, soft cake made with a blend of healthy grains, offering a light, nutty flavor, perfect as a multigrain tea cake.

info.name: Jeera Cookies (150 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | Jeera cookies are golden-brown delights with a crispy exterior and a melt-in-your-mouth texture, infused with the aromatic warmth of toasted cumin seeds, perfect for pairing with a cup of hot chai or coffee

info.name: Multigrain Cookies (150 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | Multigrain cookies are wholesome delights, packed with a variety of grains and seeds, offering a crunchy texture and a nutty flavor profile that's both satisfying and nutritious.

info.name: Pista Cookies (150 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | Pista cookies are delectable treats bursting with the rich, nutty flavor of pistachios, offering a delightful crunch and a hint of sweetness in every bite

info.name: Oatmeal Jaggery Cookies (150 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | The quintessential oatmeal cookie, bakingo style. Oats, kishmish, jaggery, cream, butter and flour.

info.name: Almond Cookies (150 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | Baked with butter, flour, milk, custard powder & fresh almonds

info.name: Almond Rocks (100 gm)

info.name: Hazelnut Rocks (100 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | Hazelnut rocks are a delicious confectionery treat that combines the rich, nutty flavor of hazelnuts with the sweetness of chocolate

info.name: Butterscotch Anniversary Poster Cake (500gm)
info.description: Serves 6 | Celebrate your special day with the Butterscotch Anniversary Cake (500g). This delicious cake features a smooth and creamy butterscotch flavor, topped with crunchy butterscotch bits, making it the perfect treat for a memorable anniversary celebration.

info.name: Party Poppers - Set of 2

info.name: Birthday Cap - Boy
info.description: Serves 1 | A perfect product for adding joy to your celebrations. Themed in blue, it has the words written "Birthday Boy".

info.name: Birthday Cap - Girl
info.description: Serves 1 | A perfect product for adding joy to your celebrations. Themed in pink, it has the words written "Birthday Girl".

info.name: HAPPY BIRTHDAY Letter Candle
info.description: Serves 1 | Candles shaped like the letters in the words 'HAPPY BIRTHDAY'.

info.name: Flower Candle (1 unit)
info.description: Serves 1 | Elegant candle that opens up when lit. It has a resemblance to pink lotus flower.

info.name: Relighting Magic Candles (1 Pack)
info.description: Serves 1 | These candles can relight themselves after being blown out. The pack contains 10 individual candles.

info.name: Bakingo Bottle Opener
info.description: Serves 1 | A bottle opener (1 unit) crafted from the house of Bakingo.

info.name: Premium Party Popper (1 Unit)
info.description: Serves 1 | The Premium Party Popper offers a burst of celebration with vibrant colors and confetti. Ideal for events, it delivers a fun and exciting atmosphere, adding a festive touch to birthdays, New Year's Eve, and other special occasions.
